\c 16 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 16\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gammachuu Fuula Waaqayyoo Dura Jiraachuu Keessaa Argamu (Faarfannaa Daawit isa afaan Ibrootaatti ''Mikitaam'' jedhamuu dha)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ani kooluu sitti galeera, ati na eegi.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ani Waaqayyoon, ''Ati gooftaa koo ti, ati anaaf wanta gaarii hundumaa dha'' nan jedha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Warri isaaf qulqullaa'anii biyyicha keessa jiran ulfina-qaboota, isaan anaaf guutummaa gammachuu kootii ti.
\m \bd 4\bd* Warri Waaqayyoon dhiisanii kan biraa fudhatan, miidhama of irratti in baay'isu, dhibaayyuu dhiigaa isaaniif dhi'aatu ani hin dhibaafadhu, afaan kootiinis maqaa isaanii hin dha'u.
\m \bd 5\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati qooda koo isa anaaf kennamee dha, ati xoofoo anaaf hiixatamee dha, ga'aan koos si harkaa in dhufa.
\m \bd 6\bd* funyoon safaraa iddoo gammachiisaa irra anaaf bu'e, eyyee, ani dhaala guddaa namatti tolu qaba; 
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyoon isa gorsa anaaf kenne nan jajadha halkanis immoo yaadni garaa koo isa kana na yaadachiisa.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo yeroo hundumaa fuula koo dura anaaf jira, inni mirga koo waan jiruufis ani hin shishu;
\m \bd 9\bd* kanaafis garaan koo in gammada, lubbuun koo inni ulfina-qabeessi in ililcha, namummaan koos immoo sodaa malee in jiraata.
\m \bd 10\bd* Ati iddoo lafa jalaatti ana hin laattu, isa siif of kennes ijaan iyyuu qilee akka argu hin gootu.
\m \bd 11\bd* Ati karaa jireenyatti nama geessu na barsiifta, guutummaan gammachuu fuula kee dura, wanti namatti tolus immoo bara hundumaattuu mirga kee jira.
